{"id": 619, "genre": 1001, "title": "你为啥不爱去KTV了？", "description": "也许是到了唱不动“死了都要爱”的年纪。", "record_count": 5781, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183551LwIDKSxOV6XoJCcA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-08T01:17:09Z", "options": [{"id": 24064, "content": "因为自己一个人唱着唱着就累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296223}, {"id": 44288, "content": "唱歌不好听", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 439006}, {"id": 23297, "content": "➕微信唱歌你听  Z13543563564", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291704}, {"id": 23299, "content": "过了那种陶醉在自己世界唱悲伤情歌的年纪", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285623}, {"id": 23300, "content": "一个人唱，其他人都在玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 819, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270063}, {"id": 23301, "content": "因为歌都很老还不能连wifi现场导入。 都不能练 新歌。  而且装修一般很土气。 还有就是 就唱歌最多 全盘转，没什么好玩的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130596}, {"id": 23302, "content": "一个是没意思了，另一个花费太高", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289742}, {"id": 23304, "content": "不喜欢泡妞了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265495}, {"id": 35336, "content": "我喜欢自己唱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370131}, {"id": 23305, "content": "老歌不想唱，新歌不会唱的地步", "image": null, "praise_count": 231, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291726}, {"id": 23817, "content": "没人请", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236612}, {"id": 23306, "content": "不会唱才是硬伤啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291735}, {"id": 24331, "content": "啊哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297222}, {"id": 23308, "content": "唱来唱去就那几首歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 227, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194615}, {"id": 23309, "content": "唱歌对身体好", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291425}, {"id": 23310, "content": "其实我是爱去KTV的", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125594}, {"id": 23311, "content": "没时间，也提不起兴趣了。在手机上唱唱，还没人打扰……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290239}, {"id": 23569, "content": "喜欢的歌太小众  并没有人会认真听?。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292484}, {"id": 23827, "content": "大家都變了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287611}, {"id": 27667, "content": "唱得不好听，都不好意思吼出来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319890}, {"id": 22294, "content": "环境总给人一种脏兮兮油腻腻的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 537, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 22295, "content": "年纪大了，受不了鬼哭狼嚎", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 29207, "content": "KTV被00后占领了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329790}, {"id": 23320, "content": "看过柯南吗？唱歌一水平。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211800LtnxM7ZI2eEKVr8Q.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 23321, "content": "EXO和TFboys都是什么鬼？还能愉快的唱K么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131904}, {"id": 25881, "content": "五音不全", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278065}, {"id": 23834, "content": "听别人唱的难听，又明白别人也是这样认为的，所以就不敢唱了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294026}, {"id": 23323, "content": "因为我不会唱歌(\"눈Д눈) ▄︻┻┳━ ·.`.`.`. ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71739}, {"id": 23835, "content": "会唱歌的人还蛮少，有些ktv歌曲池蛮小的，另外(卧槽我要说什么忘了?)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 23325, "content": "我还是喜欢去KTV 但是没有以前那么爱了 觉得腻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272158}, {"id": 23837, "content": "ktv里歌曲的mv是有多老(我只是吐槽)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 23583, "content": "周围人都不太喜欢唱歌，自己一个人又不想去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170441}, {"id": 23328, "content": "因为没有人约", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269352}, {"id": 24608, "content": "时间长了想打人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301961}, {"id": 23585, "content": "从来没去过?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194402}, {"id": 23841, "content": "喜欢上民谣了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294029}, {"id": 23332, "content": "因为我自己在家买了一套录音设备，想唱歌我干嘛不自己在家唱，录下来做点后期，比ktv那种闹人的环境好了不知道多少倍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256421}, {"id": 23334, "content": "点歌页面充满了TFBOY……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234059}, {"id": 23590, "content": "没朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289851}, {"id": 23847, "content": "没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5020}, {"id": 24359, "content": "昏天暗地烟雾缭绕脏兮兮的 除非过年过节朋友邀约", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299843}, {"id": 23338, "content": " 微信唱歌给你听听看? V信+ 527099042", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291827}, {"id": 23339, "content": "相对于唱，我更喜欢听！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291567}, {"id": 24107, "content": "人太多，轮不到我唱～人太少，不想一直唱～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291943}, {"id": 31275, "content": "唱得不好，没参与感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337517}, {"id": 23853, "content": "因为那群一起k歌的人聚不齐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216564}, {"id": 24112, "content": "他们放不开，我显得神经质，这点不好玩，出来玩就是放的开，而不是看别人神经", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296718}, {"id": 23345, "content": "不会唱。唱不好。一起去的也不一定是会唱歌的，听他们唱还不如在家听原唱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291856}, {"id": 25651, "content": "唱完一首，要等十几分才能唱。最反胃的是插歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308448}, {"id": 26163, "content": "歌都会唱，老是忍不住抢麦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311447}]}